  <body region="amara-subtitle-area">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:06.033" end="00:00:13.000">(Patos a grasnar)</p>
      <p begin="00:00:19.000" end="00:00:23.633">(M&#250;sica)</p>
      <p begin="00:00:23.700" end="00:00:27.433">Cerveja... borbulhante, dourada,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.500" end="00:00:29.333">pura, refrescante.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.600" end="00:00:42.200">A cerveja &#233; a bebida da Am&#233;rica.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:42.267" end="00:00:43.667">Quase tudo aquilo que &#233;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.733" end="00:00:45.200">importante na Am&#233;rica gira</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.267" end="00:00:46.033">&#224; volta da cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:46.100" end="00:00:47.000">Vai uma cerveja, Norm?</p>
      <p begin="00:00:47.067" end="00:00:48.600">&#201; aquela coisa espumosa e amarelada,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:48.667" end="00:00:49.500">certo?</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.567" end="00:00:49.933">Sim!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:50.000" end="00:00:51.100">T&#234;m-me contado</p>
      <p begin="00:00:51.167" end="00:00:51.767">coisa boas sobre ela.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:51.833" end="00:00:52.867">(Risos)</p>
      <p begin="00:00:52.933" end="00:00:54.333">Os americanos adoram</p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.400" end="00:00:54.800">cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.867" end="00:00:56.300">Sabe, &#233; como a m&#227;e,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:56.367" end="00:00:57.400">Deus e a tarte de ma&#231;&#227;.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:57.467" end="00:00:59.167">A cerveja est&#225; fresca e</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.233" end="00:01:00.533">a Ingrid serve-a</p>
      <p begin="00:01:00.600" end="00:01:02.167">de uma forma tradicional: num jarro</p>
      <p begin="00:01:02.233" end="00:01:03.567">com uma coroa</p>
      <p begin="00:01:03.633" end="00:01:04.233">de verduras.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:04.300" end="00:01:04.767">Hummm!</p>
      <p begin="00:01:04.833" end="00:01:07.000">Julgo que nos Estados Unidos</p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.067" end="00:01:09.000">a cerveja &#233; o equivalente a um ursinho de peluche</p>
      <p begin="00:01:09.067" end="00:01:10.300">para gente crescida.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:10.367" end="00:01:12.733">stes homens encontram</p>
      <p begin="00:01:12.800" end="00:01:15.300">relaxamento e liberta&#231;&#227;o</p>
      <p begin="00:01:15.367" end="00:01:17.333">num copo gelado de cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:17.400" end="00:01:20.567">Para eles, s&#243; a cerveja consegue isso.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:24.233" end="00:01:25.933">Durante muito tempo n&#227;o t&#237;nhamos</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26.000" end="00:01:27.733">op&#231;&#245;es.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:27.800" end="00:01:29.400">S&#243; existia aquele tipo de cerveja ligeira</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.467" end="00:01:31.233">com g&#225;s, amarela e ins&#237;pida.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:32.600" end="00:01:33.767">N&#227;o &#233; preciso pensar muito</p>
      <p begin="00:01:33.833" end="00:01:35.033">sobre o assunto</p>
      <p begin="00:01:35.100" end="00:01:36.033">porque de facto n&#227;o h&#225; muito para pensar.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:36.100" end="00:01:38.000">A vossa cerveja americana parece-nos</p>
      <p begin="00:01:38.067" end="00:01:39.867">um bocadinho como fazer amor numa canoa.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:40.533" end="00:01:42.500">Como fazer amor numa canoa?</p>
      <p begin="00:01:42.567" end="00:01:44.367">Sim, est&#225; demasiado pr&#243;ximo da &#225;gua.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.433" end="00:01:45.233">(Risos)</p>
      <p begin="00:01:45.300" end="00:01:46.767">V&#234;em-se agora mais consumidores</p>
      <p begin="00:01:46.833" end="00:01:48.267">a deixar de beber cerveja produzida</p>
      <p begin="00:01:48.333" end="00:01:49.900">em massa para</p>
      <p begin="00:01:49.967" end="00:01:51.467">cervejas artesanais que</p>
      <p begin="00:01:51.533" end="00:01:53.200">que est&#227;o agora a ser produzidas nos E.U.A.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:53.267" end="00:01:54.700">Voc&#234; est&#227;o a beber o qu&#234;?</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.767" end="00:01:56.167">Uma Blue Moon.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:56.233" end="00:01:56.900">Fat Tire</p>
      <p begin="00:01:56.967" end="00:01:57.867">Sierra Nevada.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:57.933" end="00:01:58.767">Rolling rock.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.833" end="00:02:00.000">Sam Adams Summer Ale.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:00.067" end="00:02:01.100">Pabst Blue Ribbon</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.167" end="00:02:02.033">Anchor Steam.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.100" end="00:02:03.267">Estou a beber Arrogant Bastard.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:03.900" end="00:02:06.067">O renascimento da cerveja</p>
      <p begin="00:02:06.133" end="00:02:08.667">neste pa&#237;s tem ultrapassado</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.733" end="00:02:10.867">todos os meus sonhos.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.933" end="00:02:12.967">Hoje em dia, os Estados Unidos tem</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.033" end="00:02:15.033">uma maior selec&#231;&#227;o de cervejas</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.100" end="00:02:17.200">do que qualquer outro pa&#237;s no mundo.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.267" end="00:02:19.133">Os americanos bebem muita</p>
      <p begin="00:02:19.200" end="00:02:22.033">cerveja: no valor de 97 mil milh&#245;es de d&#243;lares,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:22.100" end="00:02:22.967">s&#243; no ano passado.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:23.033" end="00:02:26.633">Estamos a falar de 6,55 milh&#245;es de gal&#245;es</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.700" end="00:02:28.033">de cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.100" end="00:02:30.100">A maior parte desta cerveja</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.167" end="00:02:32.133">veio de meia d&#250;zia de multinacionais.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:34.433" end="00:02:36.333">O meu nome &#233; Anat Baron e j&#225; estive</p>
      <p begin="00:02:36.400" end="00:02:38.467">no neg&#243;cio da cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.533" end="00:02:39.767">Quando era mi&#250;da queria</p>
      <p begin="00:02:39.833" end="00:02:40.400">ser Presidente.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.467" end="00:02:41.667">Bem eu n&#227;o sou uma vigarista</p>
      <p begin="00:02:41.733" end="00:02:43.067">n&#227;o desse tipo...</p>
      <p begin="00:02:43.133" end="00:02:44.533">Mas deste g&#233;nero.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.600" end="00:02:46.267">Quando acabei a faculdade</p>
      <p begin="00:02:46.333" end="00:02:47.333">arranjei um emprego numa empresa.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:47.400" end="00:02:49.467">Tinha um escrit&#243;rio, uma assistente,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:49.533" end="00:02:50.900">um carro da empresa.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.967" end="00:02:51.967">(buzina a apitar)</p>
      <p begin="00:02:52.033" end="00:02:53.633">Mas a vida numa empresa n&#227;o era para</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.700" end="00:02:55.200">mim: demasiada pol&#237;tica e tretas.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:59.367" end="00:03:00.667">Por isso fugi da selva empresarial.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:01.233" end="00:03:02.333">(p&#225;ssaros a grasnar)</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.400" end="00:03:03.633">Tive um neg&#243;cio de consultadoria...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.700" end="00:03:04.533">(telefones a tocar)</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.600" end="00:03:05.400">...produzi filmes.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:05.467" end="00:03:06.467">(projector a rodar)</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.533" end="00:03:08.100">Estive at&#233; metida no</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.167" end="00:03:08.600">Internet Boom.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.667" end="00:03:11.167">Avancemos at&#233; 2001.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:11.233" end="00:03:12.933">Um velho amigo precisava de ajuda</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.000" end="00:03:14.733">com o seu pequeno neg&#243;cio independente,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.800" end="00:03:16.300">Mike's Hard Lemonade.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.367" end="00:03:18.067">D&#234;em as boas-vindas a Anat Baron,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.133" end="00:03:19.733">&#224; nossa Directora Executiva.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:19.800" end="00:03:20.667">E z&#225;s...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:20.733" end="00:03:22.167">estava na ind&#250;stria da cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:22.233" end="00:03:23.733">Entrei na empresa e acabei</p>
      <p begin="00:03:23.800" end="00:03:24.933">a geri-la.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:25.000" end="00:03:26.667">A Mike n&#227;o &#233; gerida por uma grande empresa</p>
      <p begin="00:03:26.733" end="00:03:28.633">e por isso &#233; livre para ser criativa</p>
      <p begin="00:03:28.700" end="00:03:30.467">e um bocado como eu: pouco convencional.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32.033" end="00:03:35.100">Trabalhar na Mike's Hard Lemonade &#233; divertido</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.167" end="00:03:36.800">Sei o que est&#227;o a pensar:</p>
      <p begin="00:03:36.867" end="00:03:38.500">"A trabalhar na ind&#250;stria cervejeira?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.567" end="00:03:40.100">Deve ser divertido.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:40.167" end="00:03:42.233">E todas aquelas benesses:</p>
      <p begin="00:03:42.300" end="00:03:44.600">cerveja &#224; borla e festas."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:44.667" end="00:03:46.433">Bom, n&#227;o para mim.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:46.500" end="00:03:49.100">Sou al&#233;rgica ao &#225;lcool.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:49.167" end="00:03:50.933">Por isso, n&#227;o foi por causa da cerveja gr&#225;tis.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:51.600" end="00:03:53.500">O que adorava era enfrentar</p>
      <p begin="00:03:53.567" end="00:03:55.600">os monstros corporativos que</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.667" end="00:03:56.733">nos queriam ver pelas costas.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.800" end="00:03:58.833">Passados tr&#234;s anos pendurei o meu</p>
      <p begin="00:03:58.900" end="00:04:00.967">capacete para procurar novos desafios.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01.033" end="00:04:02.867">Mas n&#227;o conseguia esquecer as lutas das</p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.933" end="00:04:03.400">cervejas.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:03.467" end="00:04:04.733">Enfim as grandes marcas de cerveja</p>
      <p begin="00:04:04.800" end="00:04:06.233">at&#233; poder&#227;o n&#227;o andar a chorar pelos cantos</p>
      <p begin="00:04:06.300" end="00:04:07.600">mas as coisas j&#225; n&#227;o s&#227;o como antigamente.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.000" end="00:04:09.333">Isso deve-se &#224; competi&#231;&#227;o adicional</p>
      <p begin="00:04:09.400" end="00:04:10.700">de empresas mais pequenas.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:11.467" end="00:04:12.533">As cervejas artesanais</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.600" end="00:04:13.567">est&#227;o mesmo em crescimento.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:13.633" end="00:04:14.733">Cada vez tomam mais cota de mercado</p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.800" end="00:04:15.933">das empresas maiores.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.000" end="00:04:17.467">As vendas dos l&#237;deres das cervejas</p>
      <p begin="00:04:17.533" end="00:04:18.900">e outras grandes cervejeiras est&#227;o</p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.967" end="00:04:20.200">fracas, com crescimento de 2% ou estagnadas,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.267" end="00:04:21.733">perdendo terreno para os fabricantes de bebidas</p>
      <p begin="00:04:21.800" end="00:04:22.800">brancas.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:22.867" end="00:04:24.400">Os verdadeiros centros de lucro</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.467" end="00:04:26.000">para aqueles que procuram rendimento</p>
      <p begin="00:04:26.067" end="00:04:27.800">encontra-se nas cervejeiras regionais.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.867" end="00:04:29.067">O campo de batalha e o Santo Graal</p>
      <p begin="00:04:30.933" end="00:04:32.867">est&#227;o na sua carteira.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:32.933" end="00:04:35.133">De um lado est&#225; a Am&#233;rica corporativa</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35.200" end="00:04:37.300">a fazer tudo o que pode para</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.367" end="00:04:38.400">ganhar a todo o custo.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.467" end="00:04:40.267">Do outro lado, encontram-se as pequenas</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.333" end="00:04:42.333">cervejeiras que desafiam o status quo.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:43.333" end="00:04:45.267">Mas isto vai para al&#233;m da cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.967" end="00:04:50.067">O que est&#225; em causa &#233; o Sonho Americano.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:10.967" end="00:05:13.800">Aqui vamos n&#243;s!</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.867" end="00:05:14.900">Passou quase um ano desde</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.967" end="00:05:16.000">que vi muitas destas pessoas.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:17.233" end="00:05:19.633">E n&#227;o tenho a certeza do tipo</p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.700" end="00:05:23.600">de reac&#231;&#227;o que vou ter.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23.667" end="00:05:24.967">Se querem encontrar</p>
      <p begin="00:05:25.033" end="00:05:26.400">os grandes sucessos na ind&#250;stria da cerveja,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:26.467" end="00:05:28.300">&#233; aqui que encontram.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:28.533" end="00:05:29.833">A Conven&#231;&#227;o Anual da Ind&#250;stria da Cerveja,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:29.900" end="00:05:31.600">&#233; a reuni&#227;o dos principais intervenientes</p>
      <p begin="00:05:31.667" end="00:05:33.000">neste neg&#243;cio.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:33.067" end="00:05:34.200">Os meus antigos neste neg&#243;cio</p>
      <p begin="00:05:34.267" end="00:05:36.333">resultaram num convite.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:36.400" end="00:05:39.400">(M&#250;sica a tocar)</p>
      <p begin="00:05:39.467" end="00:05:40.133">(Disparos de m&#225;quina fotogr&#225;fica)</p>
      <p begin="00:05:40.200" end="00:05:41.567">Mas quando cheguei,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.633" end="00:05:42.800">n&#227;o me pareceram estar a choramingar</p>
      <p begin="00:05:42.867" end="00:05:43.300">por causa da cerveja.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.367" end="00:05:43.567">Ol&#225;!</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.633" end="00:05:44.433">&#201; a Anat Baron, n&#227;o &#233;?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:44.500" end="00:05:45.667">Sim sou, prazer em v&#234;-lo.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:45.733" end="00:05:46.900">Como est&#225;?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:46.967" end="00:05:48.167">Bem, e voc&#234;?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:48.233" end="00:05:48.867">Muito bem.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:48.933" end="00:05:49.867">Est&#225; com &#243;ptimo aspecto.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.933" end="00:05:50.800">Obrigada.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.867" end="00:05:51.667">Como est&#225;?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:51.733" end="00:05:52.967">Gostei de o ver.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:53.033" end="00:05:54.000">Prazer em v&#234;-lo.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54.067" end="00:05:55.400">Caramba, est&#227;o todos</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.467" end="00:05:55.800">c&#225; hoje.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.867" end="00:05:56.967">Vamos ent&#227;o ver o que</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.033" end="00:05:57.467">h&#225; de novo no neg&#243;cio das cervejas.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.533" end="00:05:58.667">Haver&#225; algo entusiasmante?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.733" end="00:06:00.000">A cerveja foi preterida</p>
      <p begin="00:06:00.067" end="00:06:01.100">pelo segundo ano consecutivo.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01.167" end="00:06:02.633">Agora est&#227;o literalmente a tentar</p>
      <p begin="00:06:02.700" end="00:06:03.533">sobreviver.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:03.600" end="00:06:05.133">A cerveja &#233; agora um produto base.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:05.200" end="00:06:06.833">J&#225; n&#227;o s&#227;o apenas as mesmas</p>
      <p begin="00:06:06.900" end="00:06:08.567">marcas nacionais do costume.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:08.633" end="00:06:10.000">H&#225; que inovar.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:10.067" end="00:06:12.200">Bem-vindos &#224; competi&#231;&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:12.267" end="00:06:14.067">Muito obrigada.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.067" end="00:06:18.633">Na manh&#227; seguinte foram s&#243; neg&#243;cios</p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.700" end="00:06:20.133">&#224; medida que a ind&#250;stria</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.200" end="00:06:21.700">mostrava as suas</p>
      <p begin="00:06:21.767" end="00:06:22.833">&#250;ltimas e maiores novidades.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.900" end="00:06:24.467">"Levanta-te e pede</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.533" end="00:06:25.733">a tua Monkey"</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.800" end="00:06:27.333">O que &#233; a Hot-N-Hard</p>
      <p begin="00:06:27.400" end="00:06:27.833">Lemonade?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:27.900" end="00:06:29.133">&#201; uma bebida de malte com</p>
      <p begin="00:06:29.200" end="00:06:30.100">uma malagueta dentro da garrafa.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30.167" end="00:06:31.733">As minhas coxas ficam assim</p>
