      <p begin="00:12:53.367" end="00:12:56.467">(Animais a grunhir, uivar)</p>
      <p begin="00:12:56.533" end="00:12:57.433">(Os barulhos param)</p>
      <p begin="00:12:57.500" end="00:12:58.833">(O cavalo peida-se)</p>
      <p begin="00:12:58.900" end="00:12:59.533">Ohh!</p>
      <p begin="00:12:59.600" end="00:13:01.533">E as outras pareciam mesmo</p>
      <p begin="00:13:01.600" end="00:13:03.000">iguais.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:03.067" end="00:13:04.400">Vendendo coisas intang&#237;veis como</p>
      <p begin="00:13:04.467" end="00:13:06.167">refrescar e sabor,</p>
      <p begin="00:13:06.233" end="00:13:08.167">todo o neg&#243;cio na Miller</p>
      <p begin="00:13:08.233" end="00:13:12.033">est&#225; de facto focado em tornar-se</p>
      <p begin="00:13:12.100" end="00:13:12.900">um grande mercado.</p>
